{"id": "1350102797282050170", "channel_id": "1350059285668958269", "type": 0, "author_id": "247436324942905345", "author_name": "littleyoukai", "author_bot": false, "content": "คนไทย = Thai people", "timestamp": "2025-03-14T13:46:30.569000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1350102797009289316", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 36938, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350059285668958269/1350102797009289316/image.png?ex=69cd21b6&is=69cbd036&hm=8ff8946e55bf1cf8f0bb89664f6c247829c51a2fab1552c93e44d92df16bf997&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1350059285668958269", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "การรวบรวมคำติชมการแปลภาษาไทย", "forum_channel_id": "1350027302205001779"}
{"id": "1350133845948891149", "channel_id": "1350059285668958269", "type": 0, "author_id": "334271675786854413", "author_name": "darkerkuro", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi, thanks for your hard work.\n\nThe only issue I can think of right now is specialized terms, such as character names or Outer Gods' name. Translating these into Thai may distort character names, so personally, I think... we can use English transliteration directly for them.\n\nIt may be necessary to first transliterate them from Chinese into English before translating them into Thai or using the English transliteration directly. Because both Thai and Chinese have vowels and tonal markers that can cause AI translations to produce inaccurate results. Especially, the Outer Gods' name created by the game itself, as there's no existing reference for comparison. So I think converting from Chinese to English first and then using English transliteration for Thai translation for character names may be a better way.", "timestamp": "2025-03-14T15:49:53.148000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1350059285668958269", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "การรวบรวมคำติชมการแปลภาษาไทย", "forum_channel_id": "1350027302205001779"}
{"id": "1350134007714676811", "channel_id": "1350059285668958269", "type": 0, "author_id": "334271675786854413", "author_name": "darkerkuro", "author_bot": false, "content": "For example, it turned into 'Mi-ri-yam' instead in Thai. <:cry:1243502872021438475>", "timestamp": "2025-03-14T15:50:31.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-14T15:50:50.233000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1350134007408627875", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 330165, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350059285668958269/1350134007408627875/image.png?ex=69cc9607&is=69cb4487&hm=f213ad51a9bf9dee737a8a2bb50abee839a99e59925d737529a55375b0a60ec7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1350059285668958269", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "การรวบรวมคำติชมการแปลภาษาไทย", "forum_channel_id": "1350027302205001779"}
